Simple study API

Features:
- Asp.Net Core 3.1
- Entity Framework Core
- Architecture based on onion architecture 
- JWT authentication and policies(claims and roles) authorization
- Middleware Requests logging (to text file)
- Simple unit and integration tests, using xUnit.
- Conversion between models and viewModels using AutoMapper
- Fluent Validations (https://fluentvalidation.net/aspnet) on the POST method
- Docker support

To test de API:
 - POST: 
	URL: http://167.71.121.156:1788/login
	BODY: {"name":"talles","password":"123"}

- GET:
	URL:  http://167.71.121.156:1788/user
	(Remember to use the bearer token on authenticantion header)
